Plotting Life Expectancy Over the Years

library(ggplot2)
p1 <- ggplot(data = gapminder_df, aes(x= year, y= lifeExp,
                                group = country, color = continent)) +
         labs(x= " Years", 
             y= "Life Expectancy")+
         geom_line(alpha = 0.5)+
         scale_x_log10()+
         scale_y_log10()+
  scale_x_continuous(limits = c(1997, 2007))
p1 + theme_classic()
